# Day 4 – Sum of Two Integers 
Take two integers `a` and `b` with constant values and print their sum with an appropriate message.
 Example
Input-a = 5
      b = 7
Output
The sum of 5 & 7 is 12

public class SumOfTwoNumbers {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        // Sum of Two Integers

        int a = 5;
        int b = 7;

        System.out.println("The sum of " + a + " & " + b + " is " + (a + b));
    }
}

Output-
The sum of 5 & 7 is 12
Time Complexity
O(1)
Space Complexity
O(1)
